{
  "stem": "11723.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, uh, I, uh, was very proud that, uh, the next year on my, uh regents, on my English regents, I think I got 94 or 95, which, uh, I'm very proud of, because many American kids failed it.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, uh, as I said, no one gave me any advice on college.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a young man I met, uh, in the Bronx, lived near me, he was going to Hunter College.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And said-- he gave me a name at Hunter College and said, go and see this person.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She's the registrar, and she'll tell you how to get in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's how I ended up at Hunter College.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this is where I met my husband, at Hunter College.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that was a pure coincidence as well, because he only went there for one semester.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, uh, we were both invited to a dinner party by the dean of foreign students.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's where we met.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have a great deal of messages to leave you with.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Um, first of all, I would like to say that I am very disturbed nowadays when every event is called a holocaust.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For instance, what happened in Bosnia is called a holocaust.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm-- it is a tragedy what happened in Bosnia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't mean to take away from the significance of the event.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the Holocaust, what we went through, was different for many reasons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One of the reasons is that the Jews were not fighting over territory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Bosnians-- they are both fighting over-- both the Bosnian, the Serbs, the Croatians-- they're fighting over land.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They all say, this land belongs to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Jews had no such claim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They weren't fighting for anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "These people have weapons.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We-- there was no way to obtain them.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
